Tools (Github):
a. Truffle Hog (Python File Integrate with Burp or Use Independently)
b. Gau, WaybackURL's and Katana
c. SQLMap and Ghauri (Please don't rely just on SQL Map, please make use of Ghauri also. Have found multiple cases where Ghauri has given better output)
d. Linkfinder and Secrets Finder
 
